show.title: Trillionaire ki Baazi
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/MW2Grs
show.description: A powerful but secretive business tycoon enters a contract marriage with the daughter of a struggling industrial family, only to be ridiculed and underestimated until his true identity gradually unfolds, transforming their pretend relationship into something real while saving her family's legacy from those who would destroy it from within.
